---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Projects | Rachel Griffard-Smith"
  description="Interactive notebooks, R packages, and pipelines by Rachel Griffard-Smith."
>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="page-title">
      <h1>Projects</h1>
      <p>Interactive notebooks, R packages, and pipelines.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="post-grid">

      <div class="post-card">
        <span class="project-type workshop">Workshop Companion Site</span>
        <h3>2026 KUMC Microbiome Symposium Workshop</h3>
        <p>Developed and delivered an interactive workshop and companion site for wet lab biologists with no prior data science background, translating complex analytical methods into accessible, hands-on learning materials. Includes accompanying talk recording.</p>
        <a href="https://rachelgriffard.github.io/kumc-microbiome-symposium/">View project →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <span class="project-type r-package">Nextflow Pipeline</span>
        <h3>Documentation for the 16Sguild Pipeline for 16S rRNA Data Analysis</h3>
        <p>Collaboratively built documentation for the 16Sguild Nextflow pipeline I created for seamless analysis of multistep data in a reproducible manner, providing detailed instructions and examples for analyzing 16S rRNA sequencing data.</p>
        <a href="https://zhao-microbiome-lab.github.io/16Sguild-docs/">View docs →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <span class="project-type workbook">Interactive Workbook</span>
        <h3>Link Functions Workbook</h3>
        <p>An interactive workbook exploring generalized linear model link functions: what they are, why they matter, and how to choose one.</p>
        <a href="https://rachelgriffard.github.io/link-functions-workbook" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="read-more">View project &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <span class="project-type r-package">R Package</span>
        <h3>micRoclean</h3>
        <p>An R package for decontaminating low-biomass 16S rRNA microbiome data, accounting for reagent-kit and environmental contaminants.</p>
        <a href="https://github.com/rachelgriffard/micRoclean" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="read-more">View on GitHub &rarr;</a>
      </div>

      <div class="post-card">
        <span class="project-type r-package">R Package</span>
        <h3>optima</h3>
        <p>An open-source R package for the Tapestri platform enabling integrative single-cell multi-omics data analysis.</p>
        <a href="https://doi.org/10.1093/bioinformatics/btad611" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="read-more">View paper &rarr;</a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
